{"tid":1463791,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【出事】難睇到一個極點 抹殺過去好多努力","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:23:02.000Z","uid":200062,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"121a136be600e0373bc44fdd6c278ce1cd8536f2","tid":1463791,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c6f9ddc35cc9d6e2d9f2e97071e84f148b5c43","tid":1463791,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"6113801643f267071c0902b6bc39070bc0ee97c8","tid":1463791,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"你班人真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"6cb996758f6327e2bb9e83a1db1c06ec6816040e","tid":1463791,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ae2c09a4cca8fcc213270bac3cf80300bf0ccec0","tid":1463791,"uid":33907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6113801643f267071c0902b6bc39070bc0ee97c8","tid":1463791,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"你班人真係好撚煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"呢啲三毛手段 睇到厭"},{"pid":"1cc4d044931be0cbe9351f3842022654069b9210","tid":1463791,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121a136be600e0373bc44fdd6c278ce1cd8536f2","tid":1463791,"uid":200062,"like":0,